# Week 4 – Deployment & Production Polish

## Overview

The fourth week of the internship focused on deploying the machine learning application and preparing it for production use. During this week, I containerized the application using Docker, configured Kubernetes deployment, automated the deployment process with GitHub Actions, deployed the application to the cloud, implemented monitoring tools, performed load testing, and finalized the project documentation.

The primary objective was to build a production-ready machine learning application by ensuring scalability, automation, monitoring, and deployment best practices.

